00:01:13.940 --> 00:01:17.110
Served my time in prison,
I've worked for the FBI

00:01:17.110 --> 00:01:21.481 align:start size:94% position:6%
for four decades and
have spent my entire life

00:01:21.481 --> 00:01:24.684 align:start size:94% position:6%
dealing with fighting
