00:20:11.243 --> 00:20:12.544
So I told her right off the top,

00:20:12.544 --> 00:20:14.813
I said no FBI agent's been shot.

00:20:14.813 --> 00:20:18.050
So I said but give me his
name and I'll find it out.

00:20:18.050 --> 00:20:21.620
So I came back and said to
