00:43:17.561 --> 00:43:20.397 align:start size:84% position:16%
so I don't feel a
hundred percent safer.

00:43:20.397 --> 00:43:25.235 align:start size:97% position:3%
I do believe that it's such
an immense hindrance to travel

00:43:25.235 --> 00:43:28.939 align:start size:97% position:3%
and I think a lot of people
are unfairly picked out

00:43:28.939 --> 00:43:31.909
that shouldn't be searched.

00:43:31.909 --> 00:43:33.644
So it's a horrible way to live

00:43:33.644 --> 00:43:35.946
because of an incident
that the rest of life,

00:43:35.946 --> 00:43:37.848
my life and other generations

00:43:37.848 --> 00:43:39.683 align:start size:84% position:16%
will have to be
searched all the time.

00:43:39.683 --> 00:43:41.185 align:start size:84% position:16%
- [Doug] It's a
bit of a conundrum,

00:43:41.185 --> 00:43:45.422
there's I suppose some value
at having a show of security,

00:43:45.422 --> 00:43:50.427
