00:43:53.097 --> 00:43:55.199 align:start size:81% position:19%
- Well for example
what I observe

00:43:55.199 --> 00:43:57.267
is the person that's
doing the screening,

00:43:57.267 --> 00:43:59.336
that's the person
watching the screen

00:43:59.336 --> 00:44:01.805
as the stuff goes
through the belt,

00:44:01.805 --> 00:44:03.574
there needs to be more
than one person there,

00:44:03.574 --> 00:44:05.976
because if I'm able
to get to that person

00:44:05.976 --> 00:44:07.511
that's really all
I need to get to.

00:44:07.511 --> 00:44:10.981
Because when I show my ID,
which would be a phony ID,

00:44:10.981 --> 00:44:13.450
and my boarding pass, and
I go over to the belt,

00:44:13.450 --> 00:44:15.185
whatever it is I have in my bag

00:44:15.185 --> 00:44:18.689 align:start size:88% position:13%
I just need that one
individual to ignore it.

00:44:18.689 --> 00:44:20.724 align:start size:84% position:16%
I'm gonna walk
through the screening

00:44:20.724 --> 00:44:22.159 align:start size:84% position:16%
because I don't
have anything on me.

00:44:22.159 --> 00:44:24.728 align:start size:97% position:3%
And if that one person
sees what's ever in the bag

00:44:24.728 --> 00:44:28.032 align:start size:97% position:3%
and ignores it because I
bribed them or whatever I did,

00:44:28.032 --> 00:44:31.068 align:start size:97% position:3%
and it gets through, I
pick up my bag and off I go

00:44:31.068 --> 00:44:33.704 align:start size:97% position:3%
and I get on the plane, no
one else is going to check it.

00:44:33.704 --> 00:44:35.673
So I don't like the fact

00:44:35.673 --> 00:44:37.441
that there's just one
person observing that.

00:44:37.441 --> 00:44:39.343
And once in while you'll
see them being trained,

00:44:39.343 --> 00:44:41.779
so there's a trainer behind
them, but most of the time

00:44:41.779 --> 00:44:43.313
