00:44:43.313 --> 00:44:46.684
And obviously, unfortunately,

00:44:46.684 --> 00:44:49.253
we live in an extremely
unethical world today,

00:44:49.253 --> 00:44:50.888 align:start size:84% position:16%
where we don't teach
ethics at home,

00:44:50.888 --> 00:44:52.356
we don't teach ethics in school,

00:44:52.356 --> 00:44:53.857
we don't teach it
in the university,

00:44:53.857 --> 00:44:55.659
we don't teach it
in the workplace.

00:44:55.659 --> 00:44:59.063 align:start size:97% position:3%
So there is a tremendous
lack of character and ethics,

00:44:59.063 --> 00:45:03.467
