00:45:47.678 --> 00:45:51.181 align:start size:97% position:3%
So once they make that wrong
turn it's very difficult

00:45:51.181 --> 00:45:54.618
to get back onto the
onto the right road.

00:45:54.618 --> 00:45:57.955
- You've now spent
