00:46:16.874 --> 00:46:18.375 align:start size:84% position:16%
that are very close
friends of mine

00:46:18.375 --> 00:46:20.677
that are retired agents I taught

00:46:20.677 --> 00:46:21.979 align:start size:84% position:16%
