00:46:32.055 --> 00:46:34.091
I taught him, he was in my class

00:46:34.091 --> 00:46:36.093 align:start size:84% position:16%
when he went
through the Academy.

00:46:36.093 --> 00:46:39.062
So yes, I was recently,

00:46:39.062 --> 00:46:40.631 align:start size:81% position:19%
on my website I
