00:49:16.486 --> 00:49:18.855 align:start size:81% position:19%
he didn't go speak
with the press.

00:49:18.855 --> 00:49:21.358
He was very much the
Director of the Bureau.

00:49:21.358 --> 00:49:22.659
And that's the way it should be.

00:49:22.659 --> 00:49:24.628 align:start size:84% position:16%
He didn't get
involved in comments,

00:49:24.628 --> 00:49:25.896
politically or otherwise.

00:49:25.896 --> 00:49:29.066
So I think it was a
change in directors

00:49:29.066 --> 00:49:32.102
and that was a problem
and I think hopefully

00:49:32.102 --> 00:49:33.804
they'll get this all cleared up,

00:49:33.804 --> 00:49:36.173
but it's no reflection
on the 13,000 agents,

00:49:36.173 --> 00:49:38.175
men and women who do
their job every day.

00:49:38.175 --> 00:49:40.510 align:start size:84% position:16%
- Well again you're
in North Dakota

00:49:40.510 --> 00:49:42.279 align:start size:84% position:16%
to talk about fraud,
particularly that

00:49:42.279 --> 00:49:44.915
that's perpetrated
on senior citizens.

